by equilibria whose stars have the same\nvorticity obey the relation \\delta M = \\Omega \\delta J, from which one can\nobtain a turning point criterion that governs the stability of orbits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Aug 2001 23:05:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Dec 2001 21:01:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
